The paper discusses a novel approach for recommending citations to assist researchers in writing papers. The proposed algorithm DocCit2Vec uses embedding techniques and considers the "structural context" of the manuscript. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), deep learning (cs.DL), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
